{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/2020-06-07TIL/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"appearance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#appearance\" aria-label=\"appearance permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#appearance\" aria-label=\"appearance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>appearance</h2>\n<p>오늘 Next.js 반응형 작업을 하던 도중 input 이 Mobile chrome 에서 이상하게 나타나는 경우가 있었다.\n여러가지 구글링을 해본결과 다음 프로퍼티를 추가해주면 된다. 설명을 보니 OS종속적인 스타일링을 해준다는 것 같다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"css\"  terminal=\"carbon\" >\n          <code slot=\"code\">.thing {\n   -webkit-appearance: none;\n   -moz-appearance:    none;\n   appearance:         none;\n}</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h2 id=\"forwardref\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#forwardref\" aria-label=\"forwardref permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#forwardref\" aria-label=\"forwardref permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ForwardRef</h2>\n<p>Next js에서 라우팅을 담당하는 next/link 모듈이 있다. 하지만 반응형을 적용할 때 제대로 라우팅이 되지않는 현상이 발생했다.\n그 이유로 예상하는것은 Link 컴포넌트 하위에 useMediaQuery(\"(max-width : 480px)\")를 이용해 두가지로 나누어 렌더링했는데\n하나만 적용 된 걸로보아 첫 번째 새로고침 또는 페이지 렌더링을 할 때 onClick 이벤트를 붙이고 matches가 동작해\n반응형 내에서는 onClick 이벤트가 안붙는 것이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 132px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/76a0b7a4a016b956a864675aaadb3683/06c4e/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.72727272727273%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/76a0b7a4a016b956a864675aaadb3683/06c4e/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/76a0b7a4a016b956a864675aaadb3683/06c4e/1.png 132w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 132px) 100vw, 132px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span> <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 147px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0d10b6cba49cc9abba114701b129e69f/a70ce/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 130.6122448979592%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/0d10b6cba49cc9abba114701b129e69f/a70ce/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0d10b6cba49cc9abba114701b129e69f/a70ce/2.png 147w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 147px) 100vw, 147px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>같은 컴포넌트이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>해결방법은 Link 컴포넌트에 passHref prop을 true로 주고 styledComponent로 Custom Anchor 태그를 만들어 적용하면 matches에\n따라 onClick 이벤트가 붙지않고 a 태그로 라우팅이 가능하다!</p>\n<p>다음은 next/link doc에 나온 방법이다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\"  terminal=\"carbon\" >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import Link from &#39;next/link&#39;\nimport styled from &#39;styled-components&#39;\n\n// This creates a custom component that wraps an &lt;a&gt; tag\nconst RedLink = styled.a`\n  color: red;\n`\n\nfunction NavLink({ href, name }) {\n  // Must add passHref to Link\n  return (\n    &lt;Link href={href} passHref&gt;\n      &lt;RedLink&gt;{name}&lt;/RedLink&gt;\n    &lt;/Link&gt;\n  )\n}\n\nexport default NavLink</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>다음과같이하면 라우팅이 onClick으로 들어가지 않고 <a> 태그로 된다</p>","excerpt":"appearance 오늘 Next.js 반응형 작업을 하던 도중 input 이 Mobile chrome 에서 이상하게 나타나는 경우가 있었다. \n여러가지 구글링을 해본결과 다음 프로퍼티를 추가해주면 된다. 설명을 보니 OS…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2020-06-07TIL/#appearance\">appearance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2020-06-07TIL/#forwardref\">ForwardRef</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/2020-06-07TIL/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ref, Mobile Chrome input css shadow수정","date":"Jun 04, 2020","tags":["mobile chrome"],"keywords":["mobile Chrome"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-06-07TIL/","series":[],"lastmod":"0001-01-01"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"]}